<section style="padding: 4rem 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <div style="background: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #0ea5e9; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="color: #0c4a6e; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">🚧 Documentation Coming Soon</h3>
        <p style="color: #075985;">
          We're working hard on comprehensive documentation. In the meantime, check out our examples and GitHub repository.
