      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Quick Start</h2>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Installation</h3>
      <pre style="background: #1f2937; color: #f9fafb; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; overflow-x: auto; margin-bottom: 2rem;"><code>npm create plank@latest my-app
cd my-app
npm install
npm run dev</code></pre>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Project Structure</h3>
      <pre style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; overflow-x: auto; margin-bottom: 2rem;"><code>my-app/
├── app/
│   ├── routes/          # File-based routing
│   │   ├── index.plk    # Home page
│   │   └── about.plk    # About page
│   └── layouts/         # Layout components
│       └── root.plk     # Root layout
├── public/              # Static assets
├── plank.config.ts      # Configuration
└── package.json</code></pre>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Creating Pages</h3>
      <p style="color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        Create a new page by adding a <code>.plk</code> file to the <code>app/routes/</code> directory:
      </p>
      <pre style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; overflow-x: auto; margin-bottom: 2rem;"><code>&lt;div&gt;
  &lt;h1&gt;My New Page&lt;/h1&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;This page ships zero JavaScript!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>

      <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Adding Islands</h3>
      <p style="color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        Add interactivity with islands:
      </p>
      <pre style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; overflow-x: auto; margin-bottom: 2rem;"><code>&lt;div&gt;
  &lt;h1&gt;Interactive Page&lt;/h1&gt;
  &lt;!-- This island loads only when needed --&gt;
  &lt;island src="./Counter.plk" client:idle&gt;
    &lt;div&gt;Loading counter...&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/island&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>

      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; margin-top: 3rem;">Key Concepts</h2>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">🏝️ Islands Architecture</h3>
        <p style="color: #4b5563;">
          Progressive enhancement with interactive components that load only when needed.
          Perfect for adding interactivity to otherwise static pages.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">📁 File-Based Routing</h3>
        <p style="color: #4b5563;">
          Intuitive routing system that maps your file structure to URL routes automatically.
          No configuration required.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">⚡ Performance Budgets</h3>
        <p style="color: #4b5563;">
          Enforced limits on JavaScript bundle sizes. Builds fail when budgets are exceeded,
          ensuring optimal performance.
        </p>
      </div>

